ut only run on synthetic data\n3. **Model Prototype**: XGBoost training skeleton complete\n4. **Data Layer**: NOT IMPLEMENTED - critical blocker for production\n\n**Next Critical Steps** (from CODEBASE.md):\n- Implement `nba_client.py` (T-010) - NBA API wrapper with rate limiting\n- Implement `fetch_team_stats.py` (T-011) - Historical data fetching\n- Implement `storage.py` (T-012) - Parquet file storage\n- Feature engineering with real NBA data (T-013)\n- Integration tests with live data (TS-001)"
